# ── Legacy non-prefixed URLs → /en/ ───────────────────────────────────────
# After the i18n migration, all real content lives under /en/ and /hu/.
# Old bookmarks pointing at /portfolio/foo/ etc. land here and 308 over to
# the English version (preserves method + tells crawlers the move is permanent).
# Order matters: more specific paths first, root last.
/portfolio/*        /en/portfolio/:splat   308
/services/*         /en/services/:splat    308
/vision-tech/*      /en/vision-tech/:splat 308
/articles/*         /en/articles/:splat    308
/about/*            /en/about/:splat       308
/contact/*          /en/contact/:splat     308
/faq/*              /en/faq/:splat         308
/pricing/*          /en/pricing/:splat     308

# PANO tours — served from tarhely (subdomain pano.visiongraphics.eu maps to /PANO/)
# Backward compatibility for old visiongraphics.eu/PANO/X/ links shared externally.
/PANO/*             https://pano.visiongraphics.eu/:splat                                    301

